textBeforeTable: Elixirs Edit Alchemy Edit Dentarg Crafters (Wrath of the Lich King) This section is for trade skills which became available after the release of Wrath of the Lich King. All the crafters listed here have actively advertised their own trade skills, either here or on the Official Dentarg US Forums. If you wish to add or remove your name from these lists, feel free to do so yourself - or contact one of people maintaining this page. Note: Please exclude skills bought from vendor, at least those up to exalted.
